## 7. Cumulative cycles

1 cycle (123). Entry skeleton land 2026-05-07.

cross-link evidence: aspirin (cycle 90, 0.401 µHa) + ibuprofen (cycle 92, 0.461 µHa) NSAID 가 inflammatory pain 측 evidence — 본 disease 의 NSAID Phase B entry 도 already PASS via FDA verification phase.
